	* gui/Makefile.am: added new source files and pixmaps, and removed
	old source files, which can be deleted.

	* gui/e-week-view-titles-item.[hc]:
	* gui/e-week-view-main-item.[hc]:
	* gui/e-week-view-event-item.[hc]:
