	calendar if it is the user's default calendar

	* gncal-full-day.c (unrecur_appointment):
	* gncal-day-panel.c (day_view_range_activated):
	* eventedit.c (ee_ok):
	* gncal-todo.c (ok_button): Added autosave for the default
	calendar.

